{"tid":2273970,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"黃兆健派四喜月餅搞墟市經濟 鄭松泰坐冷氣房食美心蛋糕玩分化","createTime":"2020-11-06T06:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T06:24:55.000Z","uid":7439,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8e31c1f24360deb02e678beb32b7bfd896a488c5","tid":2273970,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:27:09.000Z","msg":"四眼又忍辱負重..........？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0JHfC4w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JHfC4w.png&h=2aec277e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/109753481_1179245959099477_7968791100666264393_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=vc00nFfPNzIAX_RNJwM&amp;_nc_oc=AQl9UvFCqTyUBOAiEpG8DyMO_6ey9nQEfQ41rxD6qSE4ZHs8EBDYv3sJWhYp2Y_syhM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=68506eb98ea424d34df0e026a106b0b6&amp;oe=5FCA3881\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F109753481_1179245959099477_7968791100666264393_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3Dvc00nFfPNzIAX_RNJwM%26_nc_oc%3DAQl9UvFCqTyUBOAiEpG8DyMO_6ey9nQEfQ41rxD6qSE4ZHs8EBDYv3sJWhYp2Y_syhM%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D68506eb98ea424d34df0e026a106b0b6%26oe%3D5FCA3881&h=308a9bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/107255257_1176701756020564_5163093465563604328_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=u3GyKLC0uHsAX8TAHaa&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=e697735c0dce557f6c9d6b77a3744b3d&amp;oe=5FCC4FB6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F107255257_1176701756020564_5163093465563604328_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3Du3GyKLC0uHsAX8TAHaa%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3De697735c0dce557f6c9d6b77a3744b3d%26oe%3D5FCC4FB6&h=6f0bf294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日政府再度加強武漢肺炎疫症的行政規管，令不同行業一再受到嚴重打擊。香港整體市道淡靜，而且國際社會仍處於疫症陰霾，加上損害個人財產安全的《國安法》殺到、人心惶惶，使本港的經濟市場行將蕭條，減薪、停職、裁員，以至結業的浪潮或會持續。<br />\n瘟疫過後就是蕭條。熱血公民就此提出一系列復興本土社區經濟的政策倡議，包括重發小販牌照、解除行政規限及舉辦周末市集，藉此重塑昔日墟市文化，並簡化營商發牌及註冊制度，從而鼓勵自由貿易、減少對財閥的依賴，讓市民能真正以本土經濟維生。"},{"pid":"dd21012b01676f181cf2d9790ccc3058404341c3","tid":2273970,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:29:03.000Z","msg":"法子有冇份派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcc7d97230ab516febce461da46fb2970e419d7","tid":2273970,"uid":174945,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:31:06.000Z","msg":"蟲泰真係豬隊友嚟<br />\n難為四眼爬渠爬咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dee52f4c5e41cd34346ee499508809752552029","tid":2273970,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd21012b01676f181cf2d9790ccc3058404341c3","tid":2273970,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:29:03.000Z","msg":"法子有冇份派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:32:25.000Z","msg":"磅水啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://passiontimes.hk/?view=raise&amp;host=%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise%26host%3D%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AD%2590&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8ooeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=98f1d6c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://passiontimes.hk/?view=raise&amp;host=%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%90</a>"},{"pid":"9add3f3c4f28119f006b63c264a13e5c3153f37d","tid":2273970,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9dee52f4c5e41cd34346ee499508809752552029","tid":2273970,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd21012b01676f181cf2d9790ccc3058404341c3","tid":2273970,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:29:03.000Z","msg":"法子有冇份派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim